    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选前中国抓住机会在乌克兰扮演和平使者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-seizes-chance-to-play-peacemaker-in-ukraine-before-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国和欧洲对北京支持克里姆林宫的战场行动的批评日益增多，中国国家主席习近平仍在加紧努力，将自己定位为结束俄罗斯在乌克兰战争的和平使者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-seizes-chance-to-play-peacemaker-in-ukraine-before-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登抨击最高法院在改革推动中“极端主义”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登严厉批评了最高法院保守派多数派最近的裁决，呼吁对法官制定新的具有约束力的道德规则和任期限制——这项全面的提议将从根本上改变美国最高法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
